{"text_id":191556,"tokens":["In"," this"," study",","," we"," explore"," the"," magnetic"," properties"," of"," vol","bor","th","ite",","," a"," Heisenberg"," anti","ferro","magnet"," with"," anisotropic"," exchange"," on"," the"," Kag","ome"," lattice","."," Our"," motivation"," for"," this"," research"," stems"," from"," the"," growing"," interest"," in"," frustrated"," magnetism"," and"," the"," potential"," of"," vol","bor","th","ite"," as"," a"," model"," system"," for"," understanding"," the"," complex"," behavior"," of"," quantum"," spin"," liquids",".","\n\n","To"," describe"," the"," magnetic"," properties"," of"," vol","bor","th","ite",","," we"," employ"," a"," combination"," of"," theoretical"," and"," experimental"," methods","."," We"," use"," density"," functional"," theory"," (","DFT",")"," calculations"," to"," investigate"," the"," electronic"," structure"," and"," magnetic"," exchange"," interactions"," in"," the"," system","."," Additionally",","," we"," perform"," magnetization"," and"," specific"," heat"," measurements"," to"," characterize"," the"," magnetic"," behavior"," of"," vol","bor","th","ite"," at"," low"," temperatures",".","\n\n","Our"," DFT"," calculations"," reveal"," a"," complex"," magnetic"," exchange"," network"," with"," both"," isotropic"," and"," anisotropic"," interactions","."," The"," anisotropic"," exchange"," is"," found"," to"," be"," significant",","," leading"," to"," a"," highly"," frustrated"," magnetic"," ground"," state","."," Our"," magnetization"," measurements"," support"," this"," picture",","," showing"," a"," lack"," of"," long","-","range"," magnetic"," order"," and"," a"," broad"," maximum"," in"," the"," magnetic"," susceptibility","."," Furthermore",","," our"," specific"," heat"," measurements"," exhibit"," a"," low","-","temperature"," peak",","," suggesting"," the"," presence"," of"," short","-","range"," correlations"," and"," a"," gap","less"," spin"," excitation"," spectrum",".","\n\n","Our"," results"," provide"," valuable"," insights"," into"," the"," magnetic"," properties"," of"," vol","bor","th","ite"," and"," contribute"," to"," the"," ongoing"," effort"," to"," understand"," the"," behavior"," of"," frustrated"," magnetism"," in"," quantum"," spin"," liquids","."," The"," combination"," of"," DFT"," calculations"," and"," experimental"," measurements"," offers"," a"," powerful"," approach"," for"," the"," investigation"," of"," complex"," magnetic"," systems",","," paving"," the"," way"," for"," future"," studies"," in"," this"," exciting"," field","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"mixtral-8x7b","label":1}